### ============================================
### GHAS REST API - GitHub App Authentication
### ============================================
###
### Usa estos ejemplos con la extensión REST Client
### o Postman para VS Code.
###
### IMPORTANTE: Primero ejecuta get_installation_token.py
### para obtener el token de instalación y cópialo abajo.
###
### Antes de empezar:
### 1. Crea una GitHub App siguiendo el README.md
### 2. Configura GITHUB_APP_ID y GITHUB_APP_INSTALLATION_ID en .env
### 3. Ejecuta: python get_installation_token.py
### 4. Copia el token generado en la variable @token de abajo
### ============================================

### Variables de configuración
### IMPORTANTE: Reemplaza este token con el generado por get_installation_token.py
### El token expira en 1 hora, tendrás que regenerarlo después
@token = ghs_XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
@org = {{$dotenv GITHUB_ORG}}
@repo = juice-shop
@baseUrl = https://api.github.com
@apiVersion = 2022-11-28

### -----------------------------------------
### 🤖 Información de la GitHub App
### -----------------------------------------

### Ver información de la App autenticada (requiere JWT, no installation token)
### Esta llamada funcionará si usas el JWT directamente
# GET {{baseUrl}}/app
# Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
# Accept: application/vnd.github+json
# X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### -----------------------------------------
### 📦 Repositorios accesibles
### -----------------------------------------

### Listar repositorios accesibles por la instalación
### Esta es la forma más directa de ver qué repos puede acceder la App
GET {{baseUrl}}/installation/repositories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

###

### Listar repos de la organización
GET {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/repos?per_page=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### -----------------------------------------
### 🔍 Code Scanning - Alertas
### -----------------------------------------

### Obtener alertas de code scanning de un repositorio
GET {{baseUrl}}/repos/{{org}}/{{repo}}/code-scanning/alerts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

###

### Obtener alertas de code scanning de la organización
GET {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/code-scanning/alerts?per_page=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### -----------------------------------------
### 🔐 Secret Scanning - Alertas
### -----------------------------------------

### Obtener alertas de secret scanning de un repositorio
GET {{baseUrl}}/repos/{{org}}/{{repo}}/secret-scanning/alerts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

###

### Obtener alertas de secret scanning de la organización
GET {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/secret-scanning/alerts?per_page=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### -----------------------------------------
### 📦 Dependabot - Alertas
### -----------------------------------------

### Obtener alertas de Dependabot de un repositorio
GET {{baseUrl}}/repos/{{org}}/{{repo}}/dependabot/alerts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

###

### Obtener alertas de Dependabot de la organización
GET {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/dependabot/alerts?per_page=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### -----------------------------------------
### 📊 Security Overview
### -----------------------------------------

### Obtener resumen de seguridad de la organización
GET {{baseUrl}}/orgs/{{org}}/security-managers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}

### -----------------------------------------
### ℹ️ Rate Limit
### -----------------------------------------

### Verificar rate limit (las GitHub Apps tienen límites más altos)
### - Installation tokens: 5000 requests/hora (vs 5000 para PAT)
### - Si la App tiene más de 20 repos: se añaden 50 requests/repo
GET {{baseUrl}}/rate_limit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/vnd.github+json
X-GitHub-Api-Version: {{apiVersion}}
